cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new active learning algorithm for neural networks and experiments on image classification tasks, indicating a focus on machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves binary classification tasks, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the use of neural networks suggests a possible connection to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
